        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Sanchez-Young Social Security Disability Insurance for the Terminally Ill Act </b></p> <p>This bill eliminates the five-month waiting period, with respect to a terminally ill individual with a life expectancy of 12 months or less, for disability insurance benefits under the Old-Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance program.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
